OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1778097968
OL,3,CAmbulance worker takes on 126 mile
OL,4,Ccanal challenge in memory of late
OL,5,Cfather
OL,7,FAn ambulance worker from Leeds has set
OL,8,Foff on a 126 mile paddle board
OL,9,Fchallenge to raise money for charity
OL,10,Fafter his father died suddenly.
OL,12,FThe challenge is in memory of Josh
OL,13,FPhillips' father, 60-year-old Owen
OL,14,FPhillips, who died suddenly from
OL,15,Fundiagnosed coronary heart disease.
OL,17,FJosh said: "He was the healthiest he
OL,18,Fhad ever been.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1778097968
OL,3,CAmbulance worker takes on 126 mile
OL,4,Ccanal challenge in memory of late
OL,5,Cfather
OL,7,F"He had got 3 exercises into his warm-
OL,8,Fup at the gym and just dropped, there
OL,9,Fwas no clutching at his chest with
OL,10,Fchest pain or anything, he had a
OL,11,Fcardiac arrest.
OL,13,F"There was no warning, it turned out
OL,14,Fafterwards we found out he actually
OL,15,Fhad heart disease, which was not
OL,16,Fdiagnosed"
OL,18,FJosh hopes to raise awareness of
OL,19,Fsudden cardiac arrests and funds for
OL,20,Fthe British Heart Foundation and Cruse
OL,21,FBereavement Support.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1778097968
OL,3,CAmbulance worker takes on 126 mile
OL,4,Ccanal challenge in memory of late
OL,5,Cfather
OL,7,FHe said: "Last year when my dad died,
OL,8,FI bought a paddle board, and I think
OL,9,Fwhen the grief hit me I was just stuck
OL,10,Fin the house for a bit, and this is
OL,11,Fone of the things that got me out of
OL,12,Fthe house and gave me that space to
OL,13,Freflect on things.
OL,15,F"I just kind of fell in love with
OL,16,Fpaddleboard from there."
OL,18,FSo far Josh has raised more than #1800.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1778097968
OL,3,CAmbulance worker takes on 126 mile
OL,4,Ccanal challenge in memory of late
OL,5,Cfather
OL,7,FHe added: "The main thing is the
OL,8,Fawareness, we don't really talk about
OL,9,Fdeath that much in this country.
OL,11,F"But working in the ambulance Service,
OL,12,FI see it quite a lot.
OL,14,F"It's not something that you
OL,15,Fanticipate is going to happen to you,
OL,16,Feven though we all know it's going to.
OL,18,F"When it hits you close, like losing
OL,19,Fsomeone like your dad, it catches you
OL,20,Fcompletely off guard and we're just
OL,21,Fnot prepared for it."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1778097968
OL,3,CAmbulance worker takes on 126 mile
OL,4,Ccanal challenge in memory of late
OL,5,Cfather
OL,7,FJosh set off on his navigation of the
OL,8,FLeeds Liverpool canal on 4th May. He
OL,9,Fexpects the trip to take him around
OL,10,Ften days to complete, he will be
OL,11,Fcamping alongside the canal as he goes.
OL,13,FHe says finishing the challenge will
OL,14,Fbe emotional and his dad will be on
OL,15,Fhis mind.
OL,17,FJosh added: "It's going to be a
OL,18,Fmixture of feelings. I'll be elated
OL,19,Fthat I have actually achieved it.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1778097968
OL,3,CAmbulance worker takes on 126 mile
OL,4,Ccanal challenge in memory of late
OL,5,Cfather
OL,7,F"I think it'll be a bit emotional as
OL,8,Fwell cause obviously I'm doing it for
OL,9,Fmy dad. So that'll be at the forefront
OL,10,Fand I'll be looking forward to having
OL,11,Fa pint with the family to celebrate."
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
